caption.p: Neighbor-joining phylogenetic tree based on the p-distance among the nucleotide sequences of the complete genomes of Porcine Astrovirus 3. Along the branches, percentage of bootstrap values based on 10,000 replicates. Only values equal or larger than 80% are shown. The dataset contains the 11 complete genomes available so far in swine plus the 2 complete sequences – marked with a circle – reported in this work
